---
title: Festive Apple-Cranberry Cobbler Serves 6 | with Whipped Cream
description: Sweet and tangy with the warming spices of the season in the background, this dessert is so comforting, delicious and easy to make!

The ingredients and nutritional values listed below are based on 6 servings.

Ingredients: Gala apple • 35% Cream (cream, milk, dextrose, cellulose gel, carrageenan, mono and diglycerides, cellulose gum, polysorbate 80, sodium citrate, disodium phosphate) (milk) • Cranberries • Breakfast baking mix (enriched bleached flour, sugars (sugar, dextrose), leavening (baking soda, sodium aluminum phosphate, monocalcium phosphate), modified corn starch, salt, soybean oil, dried egg white, butter milk powder, sodium lauryl sulphate) (eggs, milk, wheat) • 2% Milk (partly skimmed milk, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3) (milk) • White sugar • Unsalted butter (cream) (milk) • All-purpose flour (wheat) • Icing sugar • Pumpkin pie spice mix (spice).
